title: THE PRIVATE EYE 001-003 (2013) (digital only) BRIAN K. VAUGHN
description:
This is up-to-date through the end of June 2013. It may be ridiculous to compile a series that's only 3 issues in, but this is:
1) a unique self-publishing experiment
2) a damn fine comic

If you enjoy this, I implore you to do as I have done, and go buy an issue (or all the issues) at:
 <a href="
http://panelsyndicate.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://panelsyndicate.com/</a>

and help fund the completion of this great story!  --STF

------

THE PRIVATE EYE is a forward-looking mystery created by artist Marcos Martin (AMAZING SPIDER-MAN, DAREDEVIL) and writer Brian K. Vaughan (SAGA, Y: THE LAST MAN, and the TV adaptation of Stephen King's UNDER THE DOME) with colorist Muntsa Vicente.

Set in a future where privacy is considered a sacred right and everyone has a secret identity, The Private Eye is a serialized sci-fi detective story for mature readers.
